<H3> <TI>   Roso Relieved, Appointed to Joint Command </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Roso Relieved, Appointed to Joint Command </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2704072794 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in 
Serbo-Croatian 0700 GMT 27 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU2704072794 </F>
<F P=104>  Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Presidential Council of so-called Herceg-Bosna 
in Mostar has decided to relieve General Ante Roso of his duties 
as chief of General Staff of the Croatian Defense Council [HVO]. 
Roso has been appointed to a military post in the joint command 
of the HVO and the Bosnia-Herzegovina Army. Major-General 
Milivoj Petkovic has been appointed chief of the HVO General 
Staff. 

</TEXT>

