<H3> <TI>   UN To Reinforce Peacekeeping Force </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    UN To Reinforce Peacekeeping Force </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2704164394 Paris AFP in English 1629 GMT 27 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU2704164394 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AFP </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] United Nations, April 27 (AFP) -- The UN Security 
Council gave the green light Wednesday for the deployment of an 
additional 6,500 troops to reinforce the UN Protection Force 
(UNPROFOR) in the former Yugoslavia. A resolution adopted by 
unanimity by the 15 council members authorized an increase of up 
to 6,500 additional troops for UNPROFOR, 150 military observers 
and 275 civilian police personnel. 

</TEXT>

