<F P=100> CROATIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Serb-Muslim Battles Reported in Travnik, Vitez </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Serb-Muslim Battles Reported in Travnik, Vitez </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2704215394 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in English 2103 
GMT 27 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2704215394 </F>
<F P=104>  Zagreb Radio Croatia Network </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In the Travnik and Vares regions there are reports 
of battles between Bosnian Serb forces and the Bosnian army. 
According to HVO [Croatian Defense Council] sources there are 
heavy artillery battles being waged in parts of the Travnik 
region. The HVO also reports that there are artillery battles 
between the Serbs and Muslims in the Vitez area. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

