the lower chamber has promised to give a ruling on this 
resolution soon. Rony Durand demands a Haitian solution to the 
crisis. The delegation and the office of the lower chamber met 
in camera. [passage omitted] 
  Herve Leveille of CCGN expects a positive response to their 
request from the parliamentarians. [passage omitted] 

