BFN 

    The following correction pertains to the item headlined 
"Alexander Dupeyrat Named New Justice Minister," published in 
the 31 March 1994 Latin America DAILY REPORT, page 27: 
  Column two, make headline of item read: "Alexandre Dupeyrat 
Named New Justice Minister" (correcting spelling of first name) 
  Only paragraph, first sentence, make read ...Presidential 
special adviser Alexandre Dupeyrat is the... (correcting 
spelling of first name) 

