(Asuncion ABC COLOR in Spanish 27 Mar 94 p 20) 
  Engineer Luis Alberto Meyer, the Pilcomayo River National 
Commission director, believes Paraguay and Argentina will 
require $18 million for two projects on the Pilcomayo River that 
must be implemented this year. Paraguayan and Argentine experts 
have already asked for the EEC's financial cooperation in the 
projects. (Asuncion ABC COLOR in Spanish 28 Mar 94 p 17) 

